Business Brief -- Banner Aerospace Inc.:
   Acquisition of Professional
   Aviation Associates Is Set
Professional Aviation Associates, based in Atlanta,
supplies aircraft parts and equipment to corporate, commuter
and general aviation markets.
   Banner Aerospace, based in Cleveland, said the acquisition
will increase the company's growth in the corporate aviation
market.
   Banner also said Professional Aviation's current
management team, consisting of Doyle Griggs, president, and
Thomas J. Chastain, Jr. and Jerry E. Cox, both vice
presidents, will continue to lead the company.
   Banner supplies aviation products, including hydraulic and
electrical systems, fasteners, bearings and other airframe
parts.